American Bio-Clinical Laboratories, Inc. was first established in Los Angeles, California, USA in 1984. It was founded by a small group of dedicated scientists and business executives with unique expertise in clinical experience, technical skills, and sound business strategies. ABC Laboratories is a growing clinical laboratory serving the greater Los Angeles Metropolitan area for the past 30 years. It fulfills the requirements for the Clinical Laboratory Improvement Amendments (CLIA), participates in proficiency testing with the American Association of Bioanalysts (AAB) and College of American Pathologists (CAP), and is a member of the National Independent Laboratory Association (NILA).

To help accommodate growth and to ensure the highest possible level of quality service to our clients, ABC Laboratories employs only qualified staff. The true test of the strength and resiliency of any company is its people. ABC Laboratories is fortunate to have extremely loyal, hard working, and dedicated management personnel and staff. It is through the concerted effort and good team spirit of our staff that ABC Laboratories continues to thrive and prosper. We strongly believe that this extremely important facet of our organization will effectively serve all our clients for the present and in the future.

American Bio-Clinical Laboratories, Inc. is certified nationally and licensed by the California Department of Health Services.

Selamat Datang di Laboratorium ABC

Laboratorium Amerind Bio-Clinic atau Lab ABC adalah Laboratorium Klinik Utama yang dikenal sebagai Pusat Rujukan Pemeriksaan Laboratorium di Indonesia. Lab ABC telah memperoleh Akreditasi ISO 15189 dari Komite Akreditasi Nasional dan Akreditasi KALK (Komite Akreditasi Laboratorium Kesehatan) dari Departemen Kesehatan.

Lab ABC menyediakan berbagai jenis pemeriksaan laboratorium yang lengkap, meliputi pemeriksaan yang rutin hingga pemeriksaan specifik untuk hormon Replacement Therapy dan pemeriksaan berteknologi tinggi seperti PCR / DNA. Didukung oleh manajemen yang profesional, peralatan yang mutakhir dan SDM yang kompeten dibidangnya, Laboratorium ABC hadir untuk memberikan pelayanan dengan kualitas terbaik dan terpercaya kepada pelanggan.

Lab ABC juga menawarkan berbagai fasilitas layanan yang memberikan kemudahan kepada pelanggan seperti: layanan Home Service, pelaporan hasil secara online / eReport, Pemesanan lab secara online /eRequest, layanan pengambilan spesimen oleh kurir dan berbagai kemudahan lainnya.

American Bio-Clinical Laboratories, International was first established in 1999 at Madrigal Business Park, Ayala-Alabang, Muntinlupa City, Philippines. It was founded by a group of dedicated foreign and local medical practitioners and business executives with proven expertise in Clinical Laboratories, technical skills, and sound business strategies in USA and parts of Asia.

Over the years, it has grown progressively to develop into an integral part of the medical community in Metro Manila and surrounding provinces, and has provided excellent, high quality, dependable and professional services to the medical and diagnostic laboratory industry.

The year 2010 marks a major milestone of ABC Labs, Int'l. as we celebrated our 10th year Anniversary in the health industry. This milestone is capped by being the first Free- Standing Referral Laboratory in the country to be accredited for ISO 15189:2010 by the Philippine Accreditation Office of the Department of Trade and Industry (PAO-DTI).

ABC Labs, Int'l. to date, continues to live up to its goal to set the trend in the Referral Laboratory industry by providing up-to-date laboratory testing systems. The year 2011, was marked by the opening and operation of its Molecular Biology Department providing both Real-Time and Conventional methods of DNA testing (The first Free-Standing Laboratory in the country to provide such services).
